Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好大的暴风雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 越下越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一到这种天气 那个就会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这附近一到夏天那个就会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问那个到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天咱们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓…吓我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说的出发是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们不是约好了一起去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我借了一栋草摩家的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天大家一起踏上避暑之旅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去避暑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又自己擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秘书之旅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真好啊 秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.60,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老师 请用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:29.02,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老师 今天的安排是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这边这位也开始妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透 你不用打工了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要去玩的话就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 可是像我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还邀请了泼春 波鸟 绫女 利津 杞纱 灯路 乐罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是说几乎把所有人都请了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你怎么连我哥也请了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么我非得和那个蠢女人一起去避暑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说了 都高中生了怎么还那么闹腾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}灯路 我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 所以透也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小透 你想去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 我非常想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们一定要去抓好多锹形虫和长戟大兜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有一定要放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听起来不错 要不我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的吗 来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}工作没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求你不要这样 不仅毫无说服力还让人很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起担心我 你们作业都做咋样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心 我已经快做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也是 已经快做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总是给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没有觉得麻烦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加油 透 你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 为了能和大家一起去别墅我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}推迟几天再去不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 话说夹人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他在屋里休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我去把明天去避暑的事告诉夹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要加油哦 透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接下来该努力把作业都做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹 你生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}浑身没劲 没精力搭理你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天我们要去别墅 你准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一点也没明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 明天 去别墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹打人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过你会来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会说不乐意去的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不去透会失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一起去玩吧 一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都说了别吵吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我又没说不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 我现在一点力气都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你变得随和了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 我要去抓锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还要抓长戟大兜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会了 好像终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了 这样一来一定能做完的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那只帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你的帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 感觉不太像是你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小时候我有一次迷路了 有个男孩子帮助了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是他留下的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不知道他是谁 住在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不记得他的长相了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么你会保留到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经这么破了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为这对我来说是珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他来帮我 我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪怕你已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹说他也会和我们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}长戟大兜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为是珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紫吴先生最终还是不能和我们一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等我应付完工作再过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 由希 阿夹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不在的时候不可以对小透使坏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不在才更安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 咱们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久不见 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先进屋再说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小铃 那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还没脱鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你应该很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的所思所想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的所欲所求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紫吴哥早已心知肚明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗 这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道能否回应你的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回应我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回应我 紫吴哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看起来像是那种单纯的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是说装傻也只是你的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蓝色的天空 还有蓝色的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.15,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一起来游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姐姐 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹你不去海里玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姐姐你看 贝壳好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么快就把杞纱骗走了 蠢女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本以为老师铁定会跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么这么确定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来这里能欣赏到本田同学水灵灵的泳装模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}注意你的措辞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.04,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}注意你的措辞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是表达了作为一名青少年很自然的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你已经不属于普通青少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.85,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}灯路 你不一起来游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一到海边就跟小孩似的上蹿下跳 蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倔驴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倔驴 倔驴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵死了 坐了那么久的车我现在累得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小透可厉害了 游得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还真是 她这么厉害的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到本田同学比我想象中更擅长游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过好像不会换气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想在海里畅快游泳 至少先要学会换气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看到了吗 我是不是游得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过是拼上性命在游
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 夹什么时候过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我再游一次给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别逞能了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是说过 你会被大海拐走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶 你来教教这家伙怎么换气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么突然笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样子好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起 害你下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透看起来玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最终夹也去海里玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听好了 这个世界只有黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有任何希望与可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只能在这条漆黑的道路上一直走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要误以为有一天自己能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是刺眼的阳光让你感到头晕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是说晕的是你的内心？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希和春也过来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有灯路也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啰嗦 兔小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想起了一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是个坏毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能让本田同学担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}精神可嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么快就上来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本来就没打算过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来比赛吧 比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快住手 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放手 你想害死我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}海水挺凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很快就适应啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这件泳衣很适合你 很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.40,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透一直都很可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多 多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这要感谢大家买来这件泳衣送我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 要不要比一比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有你加入夹也会更有斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才不会 我还没有你想象的那么单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算我一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我绝不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必胜 第一是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们千万不要太勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}随便游游不好吗 太孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希好厉害 拿了第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那只蠢猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受不了败给你的打击 先回别墅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怄气睡觉去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱妹妹和我一个房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 是我之前捡到的笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蠢女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妈妈 你怎么跑那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你刚才弄丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说你为什么只随身带了母亲的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么不一起带上父亲的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你总是整天把妈妈挂在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三句话离不开妈妈的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}确实是个重度母控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除此之外就没别的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道了 这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}灯路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你刚才不该那样对她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我觉得没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且她也无所谓的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么知道她无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又不知道她心底藏着什么心事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也没试图去了解过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么能说没什么大不了的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不可以这样擅自断言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么我要在意那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我哪知道她的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你来这里到底为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是专门过来为难姐姐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.57,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我肚子好像饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.09,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱妹妹 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来这里 只是单纯觉得杞纱会开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一碰到不顺心的事就乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像我心中也有背负着 有藏着心事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那家伙一定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}内心深处藏着他人无法触及的心事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱和灯路吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他俩吃晚饭时一声不吭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外人跑去掺和夫妻吵架也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最好少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真搞不懂你这是善意还是冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没事吧 我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之前也不该那样对你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}该说对不起的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么只随身带了母亲的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们永远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}灯路 找到锹形虫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今早她好像比往常都要精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}灯路灯路 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好大一只锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}树上涂了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}涂了糖水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是夹教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 夹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么早就出来跑步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们才是 这么早就出来折腾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没捉到长戟大兜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹快看 锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨蛋 这是独角仙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 红叶 能让我查一下辞典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么突然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不会又对透使坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凭什么怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我能看出来她心情不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹 这是独角仙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天我也准备去别墅那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以会有段时间不能来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要照顾好自己 别生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我现在已经生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无聊 我讨厌夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}热得要死 只会令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}波鸟 去把波鸟叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}波鸟他可是个大忙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被你这样呼来唤去也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你什么意思 我凭什么要在乎这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他就是为了我活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}理应把一切都献给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瞧你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么避暑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蠢货和丑女在一起吓闹腾 烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蹬鼻子上脸 太把自己当回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来是时候让这些人知道厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不满？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我从来都没有过这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然你想让他们知道厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如你也去别墅看看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然突然发烧 看来阳光还是太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由 由希同学 要挺住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用担心 只是轻微发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 我可以去洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去吧 你不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怕你会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学 由希交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直以为总有一天 会有一些事情必须告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我现在觉得身边不只有黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我现在相信不是我的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望到时候你愿意听我倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须打开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧闭的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打开心扉？
